name: LivingFallEvent
description: LivingFallEvent is fired when an Entity is set to be falling. This event is fired whenever an Entity is set to fall in EntityLivingBase#fall(float). This event is fired via the ForgeHooks#onLivingFall(EntityLivingBase, float) . distance contains the distance the Entity is to fall. If this event is canceled, this value is set to 0.0F. This event is Cancelable . If this event is canceled, the Entity does not fall. This event does not have a result. HasResult This event is fired on the MinecraftForge#EVENT_BUS .
